    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I did a quick glampse in the missile yamls - __ this is really bad__ . Most missiles does not override the `LaunchSpeeds` so they will stay varied, which means missiles might end up being launched with a low speed without catching up to their old speed.\n\nSet the _MaximumSpeed_ default to _MaximumLaunchSpeed_ instead of disabling Acceleration for the effect.\n"
